songs.title: Let Me Change Your Life*
songs.lyrics:
Snippet

Can be anything you wanna
Baby, let me change your life
You wanna be, you wanna be anything, you can
Baby, let me change your life
You wanna see that you can be anything you wanna
Baby, let me change your life
You wanna be, you wanna be anything
Baby, I wanna make you right
You wanna see that you can be anything you wanna
Baby, let me change your life
You can be anything
Baby
